 much easier ways to steal ideas. But in all seriousness our bottom line is the amount of impact we make. Execution is what makes startups successful. People have been tossing their ideas openly on sites like angel.co, starterpad, founder2be and many more. An idea is not as valuable as you think, you can read more on the value of an idea at <a href=\"http://paulgraham.com/start.html\">http://paulgraham.com/start.html</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Why are you doing this / What&rsquo;s the catch?</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n	We are in it for the impact. We take pride in working with startups that make a difference and we want to keep attracting other similar startups in the future.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Do I need a business plan?</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n	Not for us. You will have to fill in the application form thats it.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n	What if we have raised some seed funding?</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n	Startups that have raised more than 25k will not be eligible to apply.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2013-10-16 21:46:38','2013-10-24 12:13:14','',NULL,'FAQ 500Hrs','com.cc.content.page.Page',NULL,'2013-10-16 21:46:38',NULL,NULL),(7,11,'1','<div class=\"alert alert-info\">\r\n	The results for 500Hrs, 2013 are out! Click <a href=\"https://causecode.com/c/14/500Hrs-2013-winners\">here</a>.</div>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	Why should you apply?</h2>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n		We&rsquo;re here to put a dent in the universe, otherwise why else even be here?</p>\r\n	<small><cite title=\"Source Title\">Steve Jobs</cite></small></blockquote>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	We are. Are you?</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	We are launching a unique accelerator with one goal, increasing the odds of success for startups that should. Early stage startups compete to get their MVP built for FREE, no strings attached. No equity taken.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n		<h2>\r\n			Why Us?</h2>\r\n		<p>\r\n			We are passionat