line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Some questions that have been coming in from your fellow applicants</span></span></p>\r\n	<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">How does getting votes from users count?</span></span></h2>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Success for any startup depends on people using their product and the team&#39;s collective ability to execute and sell. Votes indicate you have a team that is eager to sell and you are solving a problem that users endorse as a pain point. Increase you odds at winning, get as many votes as you can!</span></span></p>\r\n	<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We don&rsquo;t have a logo yet?</span></span></h2>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Please feel free to use any freely available image if needed. But thinking about branding early will be helpful. What does your startup stand for and what are the core values and culture you want your brand to represent are some questions that you should be looking at.</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Can&rsquo;t find the application?/Is team profile the application?</span></span></h2>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">No. Under &ldquo;Quick Links&rdquo; there should be a link to complete your application.</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-35558664-524c-e35d-e7ce-58617d0b2b02\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If you have any other questions please feel free to email us at </span><a href=\"mailto:500Hrs@causecode.com\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">500Hrs@causecode.com</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-spa