div>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Hello %firstName%,</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3 days to the application deadline! We have had some amazing applications </span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">from social media startups, water conservation, dating, deals, advertisements, video distribution, crowdfunding, entertainment, mobile to you name it.</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If your startup has applied in the stealth mode you will still need to complete the application questionnaire to be eligible for judging. </span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can&#39;t accept not trying.&rdquo; </span></span></p>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">-- Michael Jordan</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Give yourself a chance to win complete your application and submission, If you have not already. Don&rsquo;t forget to request your friends and family to rate your team profile!</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Best,</span></span></p>\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9d6d-192c-38ba-1ef7ee050a0f\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Team CauseCode</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2013-11-28 17:45:59','2013-12-02 19:00:20','[500Hrs] 3 more days to go! Application closes on 5th December 2PM IST','com.cc.crm.autoresponder.AutoResponder',NULL,NULL,'2013-12-03 00:30:00','\0',NULL,'\0','2013-12-02 19:00:18','\0',NULL,'','ROLE_ADMIN,ROLE_ACCELERATOR_USER','','',NULL,'[500Hrs] 3 more days to go! Application closes on 5th December 2PM IST',NULL),(19,2,'<div>\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Hello,</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">7 More days for applications to close!</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Startups have been pushing hard to ask their friends and well wishers to rate their team profile. We wanted to apologize for the inconvenience caused to some of you as raters were not able to edit their rating. The issue has been resolved now and raters should be able to edit their rating until the application close date.</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">500Hrs is going to be one of the many stepping stones in the long road ahead for your startup. As a startup you need test your assumptions as cheaply as possible and ask yourselves the right questions. One of the hardest questions investors are looking from startups is, &quot;How are you going to make money?&quot;. The hard truth is, a startup can be a non-profit doing all the good in the world but if it doesn&rsquo;t have a plan to become cashflow positive, it will fail. Here is a nice article I came across that talks more about why you need to ask your customers to pay, http://bit.ly/188NbW2</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Have a great day!</span></span></p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n		<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Best,</span></span></p>\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b25dfc4-9e2c-3cf9-84f1-ca71f8ac9afd\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Vishesh &amp; Team CauseCode</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2013-11-28 15:40:15','2013-11-28 21:30:47','[500Hrs] 7 Days to go, Are you working towards success?','com.cc.crm.autoresponder.AutoResponder',NULL,NULL,'2013-11-28 21:30:00','\0',NULL,'\0','2013-11-28 21:30:47','\0',NULL,'','ROLE_ADMIN,ROLE_ACCELERATOR_USER','','',NULL,'[500Hrs] 7 Days to go, Are you working towards success?',NULL),(20,1,'<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Hello %firstName%,</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		3 days to the application deadline! We have had some amazing applications from social media startups, water conservation, dating, deals, advertisements, video distribution, crowdfunding, entertainment, mobile to you name it.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		If your startup has applied in the stealth mode you will still need to complete the application questionnaire to be eligible for judging.&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&ldquo;I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can&#39;t accept not trying.&rdquo;&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		-- Michael Jordan</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Give yourself a chance to win complete your application and submission, If you have not already. Don&rsquo;t forget to request your friends and family to rate your team profile!</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Best,</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Team CauseCode</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>','2013-12-03 06:03:11','2013-12-03 00:34:05','[500Hrs