ew Year to all!</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Best,</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Team CauseCode</div>','2013-12-24 13:28:28','2013-12-24 14:00:39','[500Hrs] And the winner is!!','com.cc.crm.autoresponder.AutoResponder',NULL,NULL,'2013-12-24 14:00:00','\0',NULL,'\0','2013-12-24 14:00:38','\0','Team CauseCode <bootstrap@causecode.com>','','ROLE_ADMIN,ROLE_ACCELERATOR_USER','','',NULL,'[500Hrs] And the winner is!!',NULL);
