INSERT INTO `cc_jobboard_job_application` VALUES (1,0,5,'2013-08-30 21:11:56','1988-01-15 00:00:00','MCA',NULL,NULL,'2013-08-30 21:11:56','Kumar Varun Varunesh','Dear Hiring Manager,\r\n\r\nI would like to express my interest for this position.  \r\n\r\nI have completed Internship in Morgan Stanley (Mumbai) last month only. There I was working on Java programming language on two different projects. During my internship I supposed to explore NoSQL database for Morgan specific content management repository. I have not only explored but utilize these expertise to a new project LCD Portal which is in prod now. \r\n\r\nAlso, I have developed a News Analytics Tool (known as Karma) which analyzes information extracted from unstructured news sources and relates it with stock prices to help Users analyze Stock Price behavior. I worked on this tool from scratch to production and finally Received Morgan Stanley award for most innovative project at Technophillia.\r\n\r\nI have a good foundation in Data Structure concepts and am well acquainted with object oriented programming (C#, Java) languages. Works well in a team and meets requirements as expected.\r\n\r\nLast week I came Bangalore and  here I am working on a Machine Learning Algorithm Implementation using Python and C programming language. Basically this is a start up by PHD scholar from Michigan University.\r\n\r\nI am looking for an opportunity in Pune or Mumbai. Looking forward to hear from you soon. \r\n\r\nThanks for your consideration. \r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nKumar Varun Varunesh\r\nMob: 07498498295',NULL,'hasgeek.com',1,1,2,NULL),(2,0,0,'2013-08-30 21:24:40','1989-07-03 00:00:00','MCA',NULL,NULL,'2013-08-30 21:24:40','Ajey Charantimath','Hello,\r\n\r\nI\'m Ajey Charantimath, an MCA graduate (2013) from KLE College of Engineering And Technology affiliated to Visvesvaraya Technological University (VTU) with an aggregate of 75%.\r\n\r\nIve worked with Mobhero (U.S based Ad-Startup) for a period of 6 months as Software Engineer Intern with the responsibility as the Team Leader of the interns and I\'m well versed with Struts, Hibernate and other web development technologies like HTML, CSS, jQuery & Ajax.\r\n\r\nIve completed my college level project using PHP, Android and MySQL. Im very passionate in developing dynamic websites.\r\n\r\nI\'ve excellent communication skills and Im a quick learner. Im willing to go an extra mile to get the job done.\r\n\r\nI have enclosed my resume along with this letter. I am hoping you will look through it and find me eligible for your firm.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nThank you.',NULL,'hasgeek.com',1,2,0,NULL),(3,0,0,'2013-08-30 21:39:01','1991-05-12 00:00:00','Bachelor of Engineering ',NULL,NULL,'2013-08-30 21:39:01','Hari Ram ',NULL,NULL,'hasgeek.com',1,3,0,NULL),(4,0,0,'2013-08-31 12:55:17','1989-11-27 00:00:00','B.Tech IT',NULL,NULL,'2013-08-31 12:55:17','Javed Hussain','Thank you for taking the time to review my letter. I am writing in response to your advertisement on hasgeek.com for a post of Software Engineer. After reading your job description, I am confident that my skills and my passion for technology are a perfect match for this position.\r\n\r\nI have graduated in 2012 from Maharishi Dayanand University (MDU) and I am currently looking for a job in the development. Im interested in an entry level position with your Company.\r\n\r\nMy technical expertise includes cross-platform proficiency(Windows, Unix) fluency in several programming languages including C,C++,HTML,Javascript,Java,Oracle 10g,JSP,Servlets,Hibernate and SQL and advanced knowledge of developer applications, tools, methodologies and best practices.\r\n\r\nI would welcome the opportunity to further discuss this position with you. If you have questions or would like to schedule an interview, please contact me by phone at +91-9910617060 or e-mail at javed.hussain43@gmail.com. I look forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nBest Regards,\r\nJaved',NULL,'hasgeek.com',1,4,0,NULL),(5,1,0,'2013-09-02 23:06:48','1987-12-01 00:00:00','M.TECH',NULL,NULL,'2013-09-04 11:05:25','Kishor Vyavahare',NULL,NULL,'hasgeek.com',5,5,0,NULL),(6,0,380000,'2013-09-04 00:29:58','1988-02-10 00:00:00','B.tech in Computre science',NULL,NULL,'2013-09-04 00:29:58','sudhanshu sekhar Lenka','I have 2 yrs of working experience in cutting-edge development tools and currently working as Associate Application developer in oracle financial services software ltd. at my current position. My background includes \r\no	2 years  experience in core JAVA\r\no	2 years experience in ADF Technology which use JSP,JSF,JSFF,XML.\r\no	Use MVC architecture for development of Application.\r\no	Having  good knowledge on Automation Testing  Tool like Junits, Selenium Id .\r\no	Making High and low level technical designs for Product modules CASA(Current Accounts and Saving Accounts).\r\no	Writing core APIs  and Hibernate for  the OBP(Oracle Banking Platform)\r\no	Major strengths include creative, problem-solver, competent, strong team player \r\nAs you will see from my attached CV, I believe I have the necessary skills, along with the commitment and enthusiasm to both contribute and benefit from a placement with your company.',NULL,'hasgeek.com',1,6,2,NULL),(7,0,0,'2013-09-04 12:12:04','1988-07-23 00:00:00','BE Computer',NULL,NULL,'2013-09-04 12:12:04','Sharda Kamble','Dear Sir/Ma\'am,\r\n\r\n\r\nI have enclosed my resume for your review. I would like the opportunity to meet and share more\r\n\r\nabout my qualifications and experience.\r\n\r\n\r\nName: :-Sharda D. Kamble\r\n\r\n\r\nGraduation :-PG-DAC from C-DAC, ACTS, Pune, Diploma in Software Testing from Q-spider and B.E-Computer, Pune University\r\n\r\nJoining Date :- Immediate.\r\n\r\nTechnology Learn :- Manual Software Testing\r\n\r\nTechnology Learn :-Java, C, C++, SQL, Dot NET., Oracle 11g.\r\n\r\nCurrent Location :- Pune\r\n\r\nReady to relocate :- yes\r\n\r\nDOB :-23th July 1988\r\n\r\n\r\nI have attached my updated resume with this email for your kind appraisal\r\n\r\n\r\nRegards:\r\n\r\nSharda Kamble\r\nmob:9552933050\r\n\r\n',NULL,'yourstory.in',1,7,1,NULL),(8,0,0,'2013-09-04 17:34:42','1991-08-23 00:00:00','BE IT',NULL,NULL,'2013-09-04 17:34:42','Jeevan Bhushetty','Jeevan v. Bhushetty\r\n432, sect no. 2, Build no. 9/15,\r\nIndrayaninagar, Bhosari, Pune-411026.          \r\nMobile number: +917276819855\r\nEmail Address: jeevan.bhushetty@gmail.com\r\n\r\nDate : 4th September 2013\r\n\r\n\r\nHR,\r\nCauseCode Technologies Pvt Ltd\r\nS. No. 120/1/2, Baner Gaon, Baner\r\nPune, MH 411045\r\nEmail: bootstrap@causecode.com \r\n\r\n\r\nDear Sir/Mam ,\r\n\r\nI am writing to apply for the Software Engineer position advertised on your site. \r\n\r\nThe opportunity presented in this listing is very interesting, and I believe that my strong technical education will make me a very competitive candidate for this position.\r\n\r\nWith a BE and Diploma degree in Information Technology with distinction class, I have a full understanding of the full life cycle of a software development project. I also have experience in learning and excelling at new technologies as needed.\r\n\r\nI can be reached anytime via email at jeevan.bhushetty@gmail.com or my cell phone, +91-7276819855\r\n\r\nThank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to speaking with you about this employment opportunity.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nJeevan v. Bhushetty\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,'null',1,8,0,NULL);
