3-12-05 09:05:23',3),(643,0,'Yes',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:05:34','2013-12-05 09:05:34',5),(644,0,'Mejorna wants to enable jewelry making aspirations for our users.  Creativity is an inherent aspect of human beings.  To be able to allow users to visualize and have it made is a highly fulfilling.  When I sold a beautiful piece of jewelry that was designed for my customers, it was obvious how delighted the customers were.  In the same way, the ability to be creative and see how they can create something really attractive is the impact Mejorna aims to make.',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:14:04','2013-12-05 09:14:04',4),(645,0,'Mejorna will market through online and offline jewelry interest groups such as Facebook, Pinterest, LinkedIn, and jewelry clubs/associations.  Online jewelry groups can range from introductions to social media marketing (e.g., contests) from using the app.  Relationship with the family jewelry business allows us to personally reach out to initial users.  With an initial core group, Mejorna will leverage the social sharing and game mechanics to drive growth of users.',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:21:07','2013-12-05 09:21:07',6),(646,1,'1) Lack of appropriate depth of technical skills to build the product (e.g., APIs, databases, cloud expertise, etc.), 2) Lack of technical lead to provide strategic guidance on roadmap (e.g., MS vs open source stack), 3) Lack of technical breadth of skills (e.g., develop with front end lacking back end experience)',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 14:52:53','2013-12-05 09:25:57',7),(647,0,'Jan 2011',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:23:00','2013-12-05 09:23:00',10),(648,0,'Jan 2011',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:23:09','2013-12-05 09:23:09',11),(649,0,'Year 1: Launch private beta of the app, enhance functionalities and content, test out social/game mechanics through iteration.  Launch basic landing and HTML user pages.\n\nYear 1.5: Build In-app storefront\n\nYear 2: Launch E-commerce storefront to produce and sell the made designs.  \n\nYear 3: Reach $100 million in revenue.  Look at 3d printing functionalities. ',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:32:35','2013-12-05 09:32:35',9),(650,0,'Yes',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:32:38','2013-12-05 09:32:38',12),(651,0,'Yes',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:32:44','2013-12-05 09:32:44',13),(652,0,'$50',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:32:49','2013-12-05 09:32:49',14),(653,1,'250-500 hours',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 15:03:14','2013-12-05 09:33:24',16),(654,0,'$7500',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:33:40','2013-12-05 09:33:40',15),(655,0,'0',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:33:43','2013-12-05 09:33:43',20),(656,0,'0',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:33:54','2013-12-05 09:33:54',18),(657,1,'I\'ve grown up in a family of entrepreneurs and have seen the potential for building something one\'s own idea.  Growing up as a designer, I wanted to always create things.  In essence, being an entrepreneur is close to being a designer and artist.  I want to do this startup because jewelry runs in my family, I enjoy adding delight to others so they can create, and this is fun.  Also, I\'ve conducted 20+ potential users interviews validating this problem and idea. ',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 15:04:21','2013-12-05 09:42:59',21),(658,0,'https://www.dropbox.com/s/jdfgvbtxgyjtg3u/Mejorna_DanielWu_Causecode_v3.pdf',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:43:01','2013-12-05 09:43:01',19),(659,0,'I\'ve attended local tech meetups to network to meet potential technical team members.  I\'ve learned more about the technology myself to be able to communicate (e.g., LINQ, etc).  I\'ve bootstrapped slowly and hired resources on Elance/Odesk with varying levels of success.  I\'ve posted intern/freelance positions with alumni job boards and other forums relevant to this domain.',NULL,99,'2013-12-05 09:46:07','2013-12-05 09:46:07',8),(660,1,'There are two of us who started PreMail and we are working on building the team and when the team is formulated we shall be working on it full time ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 18:41:34','2013-12-05 13:45:59',17),(661,2,'PreMail brings the professional network to email. We make sure your message gets to important people and they response. \n\nOur MVP is built around the problem of important people receiving more emails / invites than they can parse however some messages are potentially lucrative.  Premail helps to extract the signal from the noise with a short message that highlights a specific Call to action authenticated with a token payment or trigger! ',NULL,98,'2013-12-06 00:22:23','2013-12-05 13:26:30',1),(662,1,'As startup hustlers we personally faced this problem of trying to reach out to busy and important people but discovered that its very hard to get an introduction and email / professional networks dont work. We figured there should be a better way that ascertains our seriousness to connect and gets the attention of the persona concerned. In the process we discovered a bigger problem of making purposeful communication simple and effective ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 18:59:08','2013-12-05 13:29:40',2),(663,0,'Yes',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:30:43','2013-12-05 13:30:43',5),(664,1,'Product design & execution is what gives us the edge over competition \n\nClarity & OneLeap are indirect competitors, link clarity.fm & oneleap.to and in our process of understanding this sector we have been advocates for these services however in the process of usage discovered the shortcoming the first being a. voice - the framework involved here is flaky as it requires scheduling and most important people were simply bad at sticking to appointments b. Expectations Mismatch',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 19:01:04','2013-12-05 13:32:14',3),(665,0,'If purposeful communication is made simple and effective the world progresses at a faster pace. PreMail also contributes directly to charitable causes ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:33:42','2013-12-05 13:33:42',4),(666,2,'- We send 600 personally signed letters via snail mail to successful & influential people who need our product & we should get approx. 20 users Ref. justpaste.it/2e09\n- When someone wants to email an important person they usually google their name + email (keyword) e.g. Google(Paul Graham Email) & try to harvest the email contact. We do an ad-words on these google searches with a Link to persons pre-created premail handle Ref. justpaste.it/2e0h \n\nMore details in our Business Plan',NULL,98,'2013-12-06 00:35:57','2013-12-05 13:37:28',6),(667,0,'- Tech inputs \n- Operational Infrastructure\n- Seed Money ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:39:07','2013-12-05 13:39:07',7),(668,0,'After the product is complete we plan on joining a startup accelerator ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:39:24','2013-12-05 13:39:24',8),(669,0,'Year 1 - Get to 10,000 users. Establish the use case and create value \nYear 2 - Get to 400,000 users and make the venture cash flow positive \nYear 3 - Get to 6 Million users and premail to be a know internet brand ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:41:39','2013-12-05 13:41:39',9),(670,0,'Six months back ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:41:46','2013-12-05 13:41:46',10),(671,0,'We did a trial run and made money the same day ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:42:00','2013-12-05 13:42:00',11),(672,0,'No',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:42:16','2013-12-05 13:42:16',13),(673,0,'I dont think there should be a chare for an application fee however we are open to sharing equity for services ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:42:56','2013-12-05 13:42:56',14),(674,0,'We want an upgrate to what we have and are looknig at at least 200 development hours ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:43:30','2013-12-05 13:43:30',16),(675,0,'$ 4000 / - ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:43:57','2013-12-05 13:43:57',15),(676,0,'Yes',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:44:06','2013-12-05 13:44:06',12),(677,0,'0',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:44:27','2013-12-05 13:44:27',20),(678,0,'http://sdrv.ms/16eBrDv',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:46:48','2013-12-05 13:46:48',19),(679,0,'2',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:46:56','2013-12-05 13:46:56',18),(680,0,'We are solving a real problem and creating value in the process ',NULL,98,'2013-12-05 13:47:16','2013-12-05 13:47:16',21);
